Converting 'zoo' object to 'ts' object

Source: R/util_functions.R
zoo_to_ts.Rd

Converting 'zoo' object to 'ts' object

zoo_to_ts(zoo.obj)

Arguments

zoo.obj

a univariate 'zoo' object

Examples


data("EURO_Brent", package = "TSstudio")
class(EURO_Brent)
#> [1] "zooreg" "zoo"   
ts_plot(EURO_Brent)


EURO_Brent_ts <- zoo_to_ts(EURO_Brent)
class(EURO_Brent_ts)
#> [1] "ts"
ts_plot(EURO_Brent_ts)
